#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn48.29"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn48.29:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.29:0.2"
msgid "3. Chaḷindriyavagga "
msgstr "3. The Six Faculties "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn48.29:0.3"
msgid "29. Paṭhamasamaṇabrāhmaṇasutta "
msgstr "29. Ascetics and Brahmins (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn48.29:1.1"
msgid "“Chayimāni, bhikkhave, indriyāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these six faculties. "

msgctxt "sn48.29:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni cha? "
msgstr "What six? "

msgctxt "sn48.29:1.3"
msgid "Cakkhundriyaṃ, sotindriyaṃ, ghānindriyaṃ, jivhindriyaṃ, kāyindriyaṃ, manindriyaṃ. "
msgstr "The faculties of the eye, ear, nose, tongue, body, and mind. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.29:1.4"
msgid "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā imesaṃ channaṃ indriyānaṃ samudayañca atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ nappajānanti, "
msgstr "There are ascetics and brahmins who don’t truly understand the origin, ending, gratification, drawback, and escape when it comes to these six faculties. "

msgctxt "sn48.29:1.5"
msgid "na me te, bhikkhave, samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā samaṇesu vā samaṇasammatā brāhmaṇesu vā brāhmaṇasammatā, na ca panete āyasmanto sāmaññatthaṃ vā brahmaññatthaṃ vā diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharanti. "
msgstr "I don’t regard them as true ascetics and brahmins. Those venerables don’t realize the goal of life as an ascetic or brahmin, and don’t live having realized it with their own insight. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.29:1.6"
msgid "Ye ca kho keci, bhikkhave, samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā imesaṃ channaṃ indriyānaṃ samudayañca atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ pajānanti, "
msgstr "There are ascetics and brahmins who do truly understand the origin, ending, gratification, drawback, and escape when it comes to these six faculties. "

msgctxt "sn48.29:1.7"
msgid "te kho me, bhikkhave, samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā samaṇesu ceva samaṇasammatā brāhmaṇesu ca brāhmaṇasammatā, te ca panāyasmanto sāmaññatthañca brahmaññatthañca diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharantī”ti. "
msgstr "I regard them as true ascetics and brahmins. Those venerables realize the goal of life as an ascetic or brahmin, and live having realized it with their own insight.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.29:1.8"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

